@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rikcxr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.76)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v1 + 0.37 + v2 + 0.22)))
    v0 = (v0 * wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.93)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = 0.13
    data[tid] = v0
